name: IMDB
bio: Crafted with React.js and powered by TMDb's vast movie data, this IMDb-inspired clone offers an immersive movie exploration experience. From detailed movie profiles to user ratings, it's a dynamic hub for discovering, exploring, and engaging with the cinematic world.

name: Chat App
bio: Experience a sleek chat app built on HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and React.js, styled with Chakra UI. Powered by Firebase, it offers real-time updates and secure authentication, making seamless connections a breeze.
